<emphasis id="3285EAA6FFEE8A08FF0AF73EFE11D1D9" bold="true" box="[198,404,2207,2234]" pageId="33" pageNumber="312">Bibliography.</emphasis>
Ando 
<emphasis id="3285EAA6FFEE8A08FE33F73EFDB1D1D9" box="[511,564,2207,2234]" italics="true" pageId="33" pageNumber="312">eta</emphasis>
/. (1980c), Chen 
<emphasis id="3285EAA6FFEE8A08FCFEF73EFC46D1D9" box="[818,963,2207,2234]" italics="true" pageId="33" pageNumber="312">Shiangfan</emphasis>
eta/. (2006), 
<emphasis id="3285EAA6FFEE8A08FB51F73EFB6CD1D9" box="[1181,1257,2207,2234]" italics="true" pageId="33" pageNumber="312">
<collectingRegion id="C235F856FFEE8A08FB51F73EFB6CD1D9" box="[1181,1257,2207,2234]" country="Japan" name="Fukui" pageId="33" pageNumber="312">Fukui</collectingRegion>
</emphasis>
eta/. (2009), Hill &amp; 
<emphasis id="3285EAA6FFEE8A08F9DAF73EF921D1D9" box="[1558,1700,2207,2234]" italics="true" pageId="33" pageNumber="312">Yoshiyuki</emphasis>
(1980), Hutson, Kingston &amp; Walston (2008), Li Gang eta/. (2006), 
<emphasis id="3285EAA6FFEE8A08FBD1F775FB16D18C" box="[1053,1171,2260,2287]" italics="true" pageId="33" pageNumber="312">Ohdachi</emphasis>
eta/. (2015), 
<emphasis id="3285EAA6FFEE8A08FA9BF775FA29D18C" box="[1367,1452,2260,2287]" italics="true" pageId="33" pageNumber="312">WuYi</emphasis>
, Motokawa eta/. (2012), Yoshiyuki (1989), Zhang Lin eta/. (2018).
</paragraph>
